def filter_problematic_logins(logins):
    """
    Filters out login-name, email pairs where the login-name ends with an underscore.

    Parameters:
    logins (list of tuples): A list of tuples where each tuple contains a login-name (string) and an email (string).

    Returns:
    list of tuples: A list of tuples containing only the login-name, email pairs where the login-name ends with an underscore.
    """
    return list(filter(lambda pair: pair[0].endswith(''), logins))
